# BUSREQ / BUSACK handshake. busreq_n sampled at the rising edge of the last
# phase of any M-cycle. When granted, after the current M-cycle the core
# asserts busack_n and tri-states. We assert busreq mid-NOP-loop; expect
# busack to go low at the end of the current M-cycle and stay low until
# busreq releases. After release, the core resumes execution.
@0000
00 00 00 00 00     # NOPs (loop)
C3 00 00           # JP 0x0000
@0066
00                 # NMI vector (unused but safe)
